| A ⊓ B ⊑ ⊥ | ¬∃x(A(x) ∧ B(x)) | No A are B |
| ∃R.C | ∃y(R(x,y) ∧ C(y)) | Has some R-filler in C |
| ∀R.C | ∀y(R(x,y) ⊃ C(y)) | All R-fillers are in C |

